author: Unity
description:
Excited for Unite, but unable to make it all the way to Barcelona? Join us for a conversational, community-centric livestream featuring developers, Unity guests, session info, and more!

This is day 1 and we will officially start after the Keynote ends at 11AM CET (Barcelona local time), or 2AM PT / 5AM ET / 7PM JST.
title: Unite 2025 Community Hangout - Day 1 Live From Barcelona
